desc: Complete Filter is your one source for quality filtration products. We distribute fuel, oil, air, water, hydraulic, air/oil separators, compressed air and chemical process filtration products. We also carry an extensive inventory of European filtration products for the marine industry.

layout.text: Wix Filtration Corp, LLC. is the leader in aftermarket and original equipment filter design, producing filters for the automotive, diesel, agricultural, industrial, and speciality filter markets.
